Class CSSAppResourcePreCommitActionTypeBOMImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.util.ctm.bom.BusinessObjectModuleImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BusinessObjectModule, PreCommitActionTypeBOM

    public class CSSAppResourcePreCommitActionTypeBOMImpl
extends AppResourcePreCommitActionTypeBOMImpl
    The CTM infrastructure will call the PreCommitActionType BOM API once for the given business object type. As part of a change set transport, CSS application resource records may be inserted, updated or deleted. When such operations occur, the client resources and server properties resource caches must be refreshed. This class is responsible for refreshing these caches.
